{
  "texts": [
    "The frequency of words in the papers is represented by a 1433-dimensional word vector created using a bag-of-words model.",
    "• CiteSeer: It comprises over 6000 papers in the field of computer science from 1998 to 2002 together with the connections between them.",
    "In this collection, publications are shown as nodes, and citation links between publications are shown as edges.",
    "In addition, a label is issued to each node that falls into one of six categories based on themes, including artificial intelligence, distributed systems, databases, machine learning, parallel computing, databases, and information retrieval.",
    "• Pubmed: The dataset is a widely used citation network dataset in academic research."
  ]
}